The '''Doublefield generator''' was a specialized type of [[Deflector shield generator/Legends|shield generator]] that was produced by the [[Prexton]] company. It was employed aboard [[Loronar/Legends|Loronar]] transport ships as a type of cargo container. The generator creates two opposing spherical forcefields that serve as a transport vessel for cargo.

